Baileys as a drink is synonymous with luxury and decadence. But did you know that you could make a meal equally as delicious? We have come up with a rich chocolate trifle flavored using Bailey's Delight, currently Kenya's favorite cream liqueur, to give you one of the best adult desserts you will ever have! Try it out and let us know what you think. Ingredients Chocolate Cake Baileys Chocolate Custard Baileys Whipped Cream Method 